text: Diana García (born 21 December 1992 in Mexico City) is a Mexican professional squash player. As of February 2018, she was ranked number 79 in the world. ==References== Category:1992 births Category:Living people Category:Mexican female squash players Category:Squash players at the 2019 Pan American Games Category:Pan American Games medalists in squash Category:Pan American Games silver medalists for Mexico Category:Pan American Games bronze medalists for Mexico Category:Squash players at the 2015 Pan American Games
